{
  "stem": "6878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He used to sleep in the corn, in the field, but he'd never go in that house to sleep overnight, or the farmer's neighbor, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, one day, he traveled back to his farm, and he was shot by the Lithuanian partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Me and a friend of mine which I mentioned to you, he was in the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When he came back, he started-- he was a good Zionist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, let's go and look for Yiddish kids, maybe survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We'll find some Yiddish kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to travel around all over the country to go Saturday, Sunday, when I didn't work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to go on my motorbike and look for Yiddish kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And walking one day across a field, he was shot dead, also by partisans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you find any children?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they wouldn't disclose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wouldn't disclose.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to creche to look for them around, and me and Ida went to all the creches from Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to go around, this way, that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't find any-- any of the Yiddish kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we then decided, having so much money, that we [BACKGROUND NOISE] can't-- we saw the Yiddish people, Yiddish boys, escaping from Lithuania to Poland they go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had made up our mind that we were going to Israel, me and Ida.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Ida was really start nagging me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was afraid to stay here because we've got so much money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We built in the kitchen a double-decker for the money, so much money we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And eventually, they say in Jewish that [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If they catch a gonif, they hang him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so we had in our mind, one day, they'll catch me.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
